{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji45.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给李讷的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给李讷的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1962年1月9日）李讷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺片收到，高兴。你为什么不写封信给我呢？为什么那样吝啬呢？你不爱爸爸了，是不是呢？我希望不是，你是爱我的，只因我对你帮助太少，缺乏长谈，互不交心，所以如此。你给我来封信吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你上进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年一月九日[1]李讷，毛泽东的女儿。当时在北京大学历史系读书。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":37,"page_end":37},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}